cursion. We deﬁne the meaning of the language operationally by giving a set of reduction rules. We also prove that any computation in this programming language terminates using Tait’s computability method. A speciﬁcation language to describe categories is also included. It is used to give a formal semantics to F, G-dialgebras as well as to give a basis to the categorical programming language we introduce. i},
